to put the baby's needs first.

18:44.554 --> 18:47.341
You know, I'll exercise more,
I'll eat better...

18:47.365 --> 18:49.505
Mother, no!

18:49.529 --> 18:50.706
Why?

18:50.730 --> 18:53.579
Off the top of my head,
you're on medicare?

18:53.603 --> 18:57.283
