seriously considering this.

19:19.359 --> 19:20.836
Well, think about it, Gaby.

19:20.860 --> 19:22.808
This way, the surrogate wouldn't
be some impersonal Incubator.

19:22.832 --> 19:26.202
There'd be a family tie.

19:27.497 --> 19:31.347
I have a migraine.
I'm gonna go lay down upstairs.

19:31.371 --> 19:32.848
