after making cookies,

24:16.594 --> 24:20.536
and I looked in the living room,
and they were gone.

24:20.560 --> 24:24.169
We tried to tell her we were
going, but she was asleep.

24:24.193 --> 24:25.671
You were sleeping?

24:25.695 --> 24:28.874
