Yes, you were.

24:28.898 --> 24:31.947
Okay, all right, that lie
just lost you another week

24:31.971 --> 24:35.450
of TV and video game privileges.

24:35.474 --> 24:37.558
That's two. You wanna
keep talking and lose more?

24:37.582 --> 24:39.525
