to Mrs. Van De Kamp.

24:39.549 --> 24:41.627
Sorry.

24:41.651 --> 24:43.759
All right, go back in.
No... no harm done.

24:43.783 --> 24:45.761
I'm sorry. I'm so sorry.

24:45.785 --> 24:46.785
Ugh!

24:52.061 --> 24:54.540
