she wouldn't have believed me,

26:01.330 --> 26:03.609
and... and that
would've hurt a lot worse

26:03.633 --> 26:05.943
than anything he ever did to me.

26:17.777 --> 26:20.107
She's your mother,
and she loves you.

26:22.251 --> 26:23.729
I know it's been
a very long time,

26:23.753 --> 26:26.763
but maybe you can
talk to her about it now.

26:33.663 --> 26:35.646
I'm getting her luggage
back to her,

26:35.670 --> 26:37.665
and that's the best I can do.

26:51.811 --> 26:53.689
What are you doing here?

26:53.713 --> 26:56.066
There's something I need
to talk to you about.

26:56.090 --> 26:58.694
