27:20.840 --> 27:24.349
Well, you'll be surprised,
but I agree with you.

27:24.373 --> 27:26.697
Noah destroys
everything he touches,

27:26.721 --> 27:29.154
and the last thing
either of us wants

27:29.178 --> 27:32.778
is for this guy
to get his hooks into Zach.

27:36.655 --> 27:38.633
