35:12.411 --> 35:14.259
in your briefcase.
She thought you were gonna

35:14.283 --> 35:16.266
pop the question tonight.
Oh, no.

35:16.290 --> 35:19.093
Oh, yes. You know, this whole
fake marriage thing was okay

35:19.117 --> 35:21.095
when nobody was getting hurt.

35:21.119 --> 35:24.269
What are we doing? It's a lie!
I lost Mike over a lie,

35:24.293 --> 35:26.576
and now I'm doing
the same thing to Dr. Ron,

35:26.600 --> 35:28.603
and... and look at Edie.
She was devastated.

35:28.627 --> 35:33.138
I don't think I can go through with
this. You can't call off the wedding.

35:33.162 --> 35:35.440
How are you gonna pay for
your surgery? I don't know.

35:35.464 --> 35:38.148
You know, I'll just...
I'll sell the car.

35:38.172 --> 35:40.145
Susie, this is your health
we're talking about.

35:40.169 --> 35:41.846
We're getting married. Karl...

35:41.870 --> 35:43.848
No. Dr. Ron
would be the first to say

35:43.872 --> 35:45.850
that you're doing
the right thing.

35:45.874 --> 35:48.261
I'll figure out some way
to handle Edie.

35:48.285 --> 35:51.296
How? How are you
gonna handle Edie?

35:51.320 --> 35:53.758
That poor woman's dreams
exploded in her face tonight.

35:53.782 --> 35:56.401
You know, it's not like
you can just go out

35:56.425 --> 35:58.403
and buy her flowers,
and everything will be better.

35:58.427 --> 36:00.635
Then I'll propose to her.

36:00.659 --> 36:02.437
Well, that's a little extreme.

36:02.461 --> 36:05.310
Not really. I was probably
gonna do it eventually anyhow.

36:05.334 --> 36:07.347
Obviously we're gonna
have to get a divorce

36:07.371 --> 36:09.344
before I can actually marry her.

36:09.368 --> 36:11.468
But, uh... what?

36:13.472 --> 36:16.281
Nothing. I just...

36:16.305 --> 36:19.153
I didn't know that
you loved her like that.

36:19.177 --> 36:21.747
She's a great kid.
Total package.

36:22.881 --> 36:25.890
What's the matter, susie q?
Jealous?

36:25.914 --> 36:28.324
No, of course not.

36:29.918 --> 36:33.198
Well, okay,
this is good because...

36:33.222 --> 36:38.172
You know, if this experience
helped you to realize

36:38.196 --> 36:40.545
your true feelings, then, uh...

36:40.569 --> 36:42.807
Then we did something good here.

36:42.831 --> 36:46.251
Yeah. I think we have.

36:46.275 --> 36:48.283
Come here.

36:48.307 --> 36:51.286
I can't believe
you thought I was jealous.

36:51.310 --> 36:54.359
It's not like I still have
feelings for you anymore.

36:54.383 --> 36:58.223
You're right.
I-I was just fooling around.

37:01.350 --> 37:03.798
So? How did it go?

37:03.822 --> 37:07.302
Fine. I just dropped off
the luggage and left.

37:07.326 --> 37:08.456
Oh.

37:14.663 --> 37:16.273
Mmm.

37:18.367 --> 37:20.415
What was that for?

37:20.439 --> 37:23.388
No reason.

37:23.412 --> 37:25.390
Hey, I was thinking...

37:25.414 --> 37:28.253
Weshould look into adoption.

37:28.277 --> 37:31.296
Seriously? Mm-hmm.

37:31.320 --> 37:34.329
But I thought you wanted
a kid with your own d.N.A.?

37:34.353 --> 37:36.863
Blood isn't everything.

37:42.361 --> 37:44.361
Mmm.

37:57.376 --> 37:58.446
Hey!

37:59.978 --> 38:02.256
I heard ya lost
your kids yesterday.

38:02.280 --> 38:03.558
Yeah.

38:03.582 --> 38:06.566
It was cleared up.
It was just a little confusion.

38:06.590 --> 38:08.733
Uh, help me out here
with something.

38:08.757 --> 38:11.536
What exactly is it
you look for in a baby-sitter?

38:11.560 --> 38:12.697
Excuse me?

38:12.721 --> 38:15.440
Well, I may be ancient,
like you say,

38:15.464 --> 38:18.443
but I've never gotten drunk
and lost track of three kids.

38:18.467 --> 38:19.404
What?

38:19.428 --> 38:21.406
I smelled wine
on Bree Van De Kamp

38:21.430 --> 38:23.578
when she was looking
for your boys.

38:23.602 --> 38:25.780
That's ridiculous. Is it?

38:25.804 --> 38:28.418
Yesterday I found her passed out
on her front lawn,

38:28.442 --> 38:31.416
drunk as a skunk. I've known
Bree for years and years.

38:31.440 --> 38:33.918
There's no way she was drinking
while baby-sitting my kids.

38:33.942 --> 38:36.996
So... just go spread your poison
somewhere else. Okay?

38:37.020 --> 38:39.594
I just thought I'd do you
a favor and let you know,

38:39.618 --> 38:40.595
that's all.

38:40.619 --> 38:42.389
Okay, well, thanks.

38:47.826 --> 38:50.304
Hi.

38:50.328 --> 38:54.809
You, um, you recovered from
all of yesterday's excitement?

38:54.833 --> 38:57.850
Oh, truthfully, I haven't been
able to get my mind off it.

38:57.874 --> 38:59.344
What a scare, huh?

38:59.368 --> 39:02.847
Yeah, although
I-I still can't figure out

39:02.871 --> 39:05.641
how my boys
managed to sneak past you.

39:07.516 --> 39:09.394
Well, you know
how boys are at the age.

39:09.418 --> 39:10.895
They're escape artists.

39:10.919 --> 39:13.498
They're like lightning.

39:13.522 --> 39:14.859
It's just, penny...

39:14.883 --> 39:16.601
Penny?

39:16.625 --> 39:18.733
Well, I mean,
I just don't understand

39:18.757 --> 39:22.106
how Porter and Preston managed
to wrangle her into the stroller

39:22.130 --> 39:24.369
and then make it out
your front door

39:24.393 --> 39:26.441
without you even noticing.

39:33.972 --> 39:36.621
I guess
if you'd fallen asleep...

39:36.645 --> 39:38.523
It could've happened
like that, I-I guess.

39:38.547 --> 39:40.024
You know, I think, um,

39:40.048 --> 39:42.126
I must have been cleaning
the kitchen,

39:42.150 --> 39:44.389
and I-I just didn't hear them

39:44.413 --> 39:47.100
because of the noise
from the dishwasher.

39:47.124 --> 39:51.466
Look, I apologize in advance
for how this is going to sound,

39:51.490 --> 39:54.138
but I have to ask. It's just
gonna eat away at me.

39:54.162 --> 39:56.879
Were you drinking
while baby-sitting my kids?

39:56.903 --> 39:58.165
No!

40:02.531 --> 40:04.479
Oh...

40:04.503 --> 40:06.481
You know, I may have had

40:06.505 --> 40:09.984
just the tiniest little bit
of chardonnay.

40:10.008 --> 40:14.789
Oh, gosh, you got drunk,
and you passed out.

40:14.813 --> 40:17.396
Lynette, if I close my eyes
even for a moment,

40:17.420 --> 40:19.894
it's because of these
antihistamines I've been taking.

40:19.918 --> 40:21.065
Really?

40:21.089 --> 40:23.668
Is that why you passed out
on your front lawn

40:23.692 --> 40:25.470
yesterday morning?

40:25.494 --> 40:28.478
Now that you're speaking to me
in a fairly accusatory tone,

40:28.502 --> 40:30.975
may I remind you that
I was doing you a favor?

40:30.999 --> 40:33.478
You put my kids in danger,
and then you lied about it.

40:33.502 --> 40:35.480
Do you not get how big that is?

40:35.504 --> 40:37.487
Do you have some
kind of problem with alcohol?

40:37.511 --> 40:39.814
No! The only problem I have
is with your children.

40:39.838 --> 40:42.517
They're incorrigible
because you let them run amok.

40:42.541 --> 40:43.818
And if I hadn't drifted off,

40:43.842 --> 40:45.990
they would have waited
until I was in the bathroom

40:46.014 --> 40:48.531
or stuck on the phone
or upstairs doing laundry.

40:48.555 --> 40:50.024
On any given day,

40:50.048 --> 40:53.148
how many glasses of wine
do you put away?

40:56.454 --> 40:58.671
I will not be spoken to
like that.

40:58.695 --> 41:00.557
I just won't.

41:19.948 --> 41:22.848
Now and then,
we allneed a little help...

41:25.554 --> 41:28.863
So we ask for small favors.

41:28.887 --> 41:31.596
Thanks. I owe you one.

41:31.620 --> 41:33.097
But it's always best

41:33.121 --> 41:36.641
to be wary of those eager
to come to our rescue.

41:36.665 --> 41:38.765
Well, go on. Kiss the bride.

41:45.534 --> 41:47.761
Because even the smallest
of favors...

41:47.785 --> 41:51.756
Sure thing, Tom. I'd be happy
to baby-sit for you.

41:51.780 --> 41:55.059
My, have you noticed
how clogged my rain gutters are?

41:55.083 --> 41:57.822
Carries a price tag.

41:57.846 --> 42:00.595
Yes, everyone has an agenda.

42:00.619 --> 42:02.597
I heard about your operation,
aunt Inez,

42:02.621 --> 42:04.599
and I'm jumping
on a plane right now

42:04.623 --> 42:06.601
to come and help you out.

42:06.625 --> 42:08.603
No matter what they may tell us.

42:08.627 --> 42:10.805
No, I'm happy to,

42:10.829 --> 42:15.740
and I'm prepared to stay
as long as it takes.

42:15.764 --> 42:17.982
And in those rare instances

42:18.006 --> 42:21.245
where thereis
no ulterior motive,

42:21.269 --> 42:22.917
we're so taken aback

42:22.941 --> 42:25.671
that we may fail
to recognize the truth...

42:38.887 --> 42:41.887
That a loving friend has just
done us an enormous favor.
